-----------------
SortedMap is an interface which extends Map, tree is an implementation of navigable map, navigable map extends sorted map(interface)
sorts based on keys, either by natural ordering or by spefied comparator.

tree map time complexity is O(n) for inserting , getting is O(1) and for contains and all it is o(n)
----------------------------------
unbalanced BST tree---
right side higher values, left side lower values